data.description: NEW EXTERIOR PAINT...looks beautiful!!!  Great property, in town, super private setting, and a fun place to live!!!  This is a 1892SF Block-built home with 3 bedrooms/2 baths and a 2 car carport with plenty of additional parking for you and your company, even an RV!!!  Enjoy a large Living Area, Dining Room, DEN with wood-burning fireplace, BONUS Room with adjoining Office, and full-length AZ Room, and the best part is there's a beautiful pool and Cabana area with BBQ, and lawn to enjoy your sanctuary!!!  Oh, and BONUS...there's a separate Theatre Room on the property for additional fun!!!  The property also features a fabulous Mesquite tree in the front for your privacy and Oleanders all along the back...ready for you and your family to move in and enjoy all the wonderful features!!!
